Ticket Number: 00424453
Ticket Subject: SharePoint Online Reporting
Ticket Details: We categorize our SharePoint scans into four site collection groups: Communication, Teams, Personal, and Others. The reports within the console categorize the data collected from scans by SharePoint, Teams, and OneDrive. Is there a way to edit/create reports that show data reflecting how we categorize our sites? We'd also like show the total percentage breakdown of sensitive data by site collection.

Thank you!
